b3ce9b10446bf5246711981099","tid":299642,"uid":54993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"無息派, 星期一預計又沽一轉落去"},{"pid":"3ec94a87f58e00a3abec31810297fb854f378bd9","tid":299642,"uid":38417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢盤數有啲不明白想請教<br />\n1. 有一個大銀碼的資產是投資人壽保險，他不是計開支，有點怪<br />\n2. 行政費用大幅上升<br />\n3. 有間子公司分左$8,000萬股息走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時唔識答, 我試下去查資料, 一齊學下野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩查左, 預付左既保險係當資產, <br />\n期期比既係當支出<br />\n<br />\n其實creative elite = 陳氐均成, 暫時睇唔到佢有其他業務,  以家d 新股興將上市前既資金派比自己食番, 唔想同新股東分享以前賺既錢, 將上市既資產淨值比降至50%左右甚至更低, 佢食左80m, 又集資88m,<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  , 你話佢上市昆水, 賣殼賺錢又得, 睇你點認為<br />\n<br />\n行政費我唔識答<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得有錯歡迎討論"},{"pid":"b0c19b4c5aec6f42db05c8ba9d9aab9074ab0500","tid":299642,"uid":48006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1633/ZH_TW/002850335-0.PDF&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE&amp;usg=AFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fiis.quamnet.com%2Fmedia%2FIRAnnouncement%2F1633%2FZH_TW%2F002850335-0.PDF%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE%26usg%3DAFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog&d=vkb9cU1le4sf79eUvImRpo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f9408e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1633/ZH_TW/002850335-0.PDF&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE&amp;usg=AFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業績</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9up下先<br />\nPE 8,  現值估值ok 既, <br />\n預計星期一同之後會跌去0.4左右<br />\n同埋個應收款項咁大, 有水份都唔定<br />\n最近上市d 錢買器材多, 如果林鄭起多d 公屋居屋,<br />\n將來都有機會賺多d 既, 但建築行業步入衰退期,<br />\n真係難講<br />\n<br />\n最後,<br />\n睇埋之後個ccass 再決定認唔認輸先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時輸咪坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非有更好嘅股買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暴跌後反彈唔算多,  如果價位穩定, 亦可以坐下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點為之穩定...無成交既話唔上唔落或者好大機會陰陰咁跌<br />\n<br />\n其實好矛盾.."},{"pid":"90f045fe9c992ba0843530222e05cdd6aa0ab582","tid":299642,"uid":65026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1633/ZH_TW/002850335-0.PDF&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE&amp;usg=AFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fiis.quamnet.com%2Fmedia%2FIRAnnouncement%2F1633%2FZH_TW%2F002850335-0.PDF%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE%26usg%3DAFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog&d=vkb9cU1le4sf79eUvImRpo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f9408e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://iis.quamnet.com/media/IRAnnouncement/1633/ZH_TW/002850335-0.PDF&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiK85H8zOXUAhUJl5QKHXB9Cd0QFggeMAE&amp;usg=AFQjCNElZ_KsTHVqA0IHQ7R4prd3zWGfog</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業績</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9up下先<br />\nPE 8,  現值估值ok 既, <br />\n預計星期一同之後會跌去0.4左右<br />\n同埋個應收款項咁大, 有水份都唔定<br />\n最近上市d 錢買器材多, 如果林鄭起多d 公屋居屋,<br />\n將來都有機會賺多d 既, 但建築行業步入衰退期,<br />\n真係難講<br />\n<br />\n最後,<br />\n睇埋之後個ccass 再決定認唔認輸先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時輸咪坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非有更